request.description:
### Delete Admin User

This endpoint is used by admin to delete any user by username (case sensitive)! Requires admin auth.

#### Request Body

- username (string, required): The username of the admin user to be deleted.


#### Response

The response for this request is a JSON object with a key "message" which may contain a message indicating the status of the deletion.

#### JSON Schema

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

### Refresh Account Access Token

This endpoint allows the user to refresh the access token by providing a valid refresh token.

**Request Body**

- refresh token (string, required): The refresh token used to obtain a new access token.


**Response**  
The response of this request can be documented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "accessToken": {
            "type": "string"
        }
    }
}

 ```

**Related Responses**

- { "accessToken": { "type": "string" }}

- { "updated_user": { "type": "object", "properties": { "username": { "type": "string" }, "firstName": { "type": "string" }, "lastName": { "type": "string" }, "email": { "type": "string" }, "avatar": { "type": "string" }, "phoneNumber": { "type": "string" }, "role": { "type": "string" }, "createdAt": { "type": "string" }, "updatedAt": { "type": "string" }, "deleted": { "type": "boolean" } } }}

